transcript:
Customer: Aaye mere dil ko dekho kabhi, aaye na khud batayega kaise ho tum, dil se da tumse yuhi nahi ho.
Hello
Arre sir kyu mat kar rahe ho bataiye.
Ha wo ho gaya na sir.
Ha sir abhi process kar rahe hai.
Hello
Ha sir.
Customer: Ye nahi aa raha.
Executive: Ha boliye.
Customer: Ha mai keh raha hu process karenge apni side se kuch dino me aapke paas aa jayega.
Customer: Ho gaya process ho gaya na?
Executive: Process abhi aaj dal do process ke liye.
Customer: Kya hua?
Executive: Abhi dalenge process ke liye us din to late ho gaya tha na band ho gaya tha office 6 baje.
Customer: Aisa hai.
Executive: Wo mobile me thoda problem ho gaya tha wo mobile kya hai thoda kaam nahi kar raha tha iske liye.
Executive: Koi baat nahi wo to waise bhi us din wo bhi kya tha fir do din off ho gaya Saturday Sunday.
Customer: Ha ha.
Executive: Ha abhi kar denge.
Executive: Lagenge kuch din lagenge aapko update karta rahunga ya aap call karke puchh lo koi dikkat nahi hai, theek hai? Aur ho jayega abhi ye ho gaya unse baat ho gayi hai to ho jayega.
Customer: Hai na? Okay okay.
Executive: Ha.
Executive: Sab tak use kar rahe ho na sir business?
Customer: Kya hua?
Executive: Sab tak use kar rahe ho na sir business?
Customer: Dekhte hai lekin kuch ho nahi pa raha hai yaar sir.
Executive: Ha sir agar nahi ho pa raha hai isliye karwa rahe ho aap dekhiye tab tak apni leads vagaira lete raho.
Customer: Hai na? Kyunki chalu to hai hi wo waste karne se kya fayda koi convert ho jaye to ho jaye.
Executive: Ha.
Executive: Baki wo doubt to nahi hai aapke mind me kuch ki iske baad bhi inquiries vagaira aata rahega wo bhi abhi clear kar deta hu mai wo sab nahi aayega sir.
Customer: Kya hua?
Executive: Wo kuch doubt to nahi hai aapke mind me ki iske baad bhi inquiries vagaira aati rahengi?
Customer: Nahi nahi waha koi dikkat nahi waha tak nahi chalega.
Executive: Ha wahi kyuki aap keh rahe the ki wo inquiries band ho jati hai na.
Customer: Nahi aa raha.
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Koi baat nahi waha tak nahi.
Executive: Theek hai sir.
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Okay okay.
